description: Searches group profiles in Amazon DataZone.

parameters.name: domainIdentifier
parameters.description: The identifier of the Amazon DataZone domain in which you want to search group profiles.

parameters.name: groupType
parameters.description: The group type for which to search.

nested_items.name: items
nested_items.description: The results of the SearchGroupProfiles action.

nested_items.name: domainId
nested_items.description: The ID of the Amazon DataZone domain of a group profile.

nested_items.name: groupName
nested_items.description: The group name of a group profile.

nested_items.name: id
nested_items.description: The ID of a group profile.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The status of a group profile.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: When the number of results is greater than the default value for the MaxResults parameter, or if you explicitly specify a value for MaxResults that is less than the number of results, the response includes a pagination token named NextToken. You can specify this NextToken value in a subsequent call to SearchGroupProfiles to list the next set of results.
